<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="17Oct1940"><font color="red">17 October 1940</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Edmund Brauchbar): I have written the U.S. Legation at Berne to find whether I shall have the same difficulties with the State Department if and when I reach Switzerland. </div>
